<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #222; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <div style="border-left: 6px solid #d41121; padding: 12px 16px; background: #ffffff;">
    <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #d41121; font-size: 16px;">
      <strong>ANPMP AGM/Scientific Conference – Attendance Moderator Invite</strong>
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 8px 0;">
      You have been invited to serve as an <strong>Attendance Moderator</strong> for the ANPMP AGM/Scientific Conference.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 8px 0;">
      As a moderator, you will be responsible for scanning delegate QR codes and marking attendance on each conference day.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 16px 0 8px 0;">
      Click the button below to set up your password and activate your account:
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <a href="{{inviteUrl}}"
         style="background-color: #d41121; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">
        Set Up My Account
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="margin: 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #555;">
      Or copy this link into your browser:<br />
      <a href="{{inviteUrl}}" style="color: #d41121; word-break: break-all;">{{inviteUrl}}</a>
    </p>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 16px 0;" />

    <p style="margin: 8px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #888;">
      This invite link will expire in <strong>7 days</strong>. If you did not expect this email, please ignore it or contact the conference team.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
